text: Jacques Landry (27 September 1911 - 24 November 1976) was a Canadian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Canadian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Canada Category:Ski jumpers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa
